      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="pillar-bullets">
      <li class="reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 100ms;">Early visibility into spin-outs, pilot projects, and translational teams<InlineCitation {...citations.stanfordPilot} /></li>
      <li class="reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 200ms;">Access to key investigators and clinical trial infrastructure<InlineCitation {...citations.stanfordLongevity} /><InlineCitation {...citations.cedarsAging} /></li>
